title: Electronic tray filling machine
summary: Electronic tray filling machine filling 500 trays per hour, conveyor compatible.

eligible.eligibleBullet01: be an electronic tray filling machine
eligible.eligibleBullet02: fill polystyrene trays, plug trays, shuttle trays and pots in trays
eligible.eligibleBullet04: be able to change filling density to achieve optimal compaction for different seeding requirements
eligible.eligibleBullet05: be able of handling 600mm x 400mm trays
eligible.eligibleBullet06: be compatible with a conveyor belt system to allow incorporation into a fully automated seeding line or transplanting line
